      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW ULTRA (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (30.53) in a Grade 4 at The Meadows. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Worth another chance. PAW CLARISSA (8) has an excellent record here having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (22.47) in a Free For All last time at this track. Can feature in the finish. FEAR THE BEER (4) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Filled the minor placings over 450m at Shepparton (25.12) in a Special conditions race but is better placed at the shorter trip here. Has a strong winning record at this journey including eight wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Must be included in calculations. MASSETER (2) missed the frame latest (22.71) when fifth over 390m at this track in a Mix 3/4. Already a winner from this draw.",
